            <lg xml:id="TK1314">
<l>yāriṉuṅ kātala meṉṟēṉā vūṭiṉāḷ</l>
<l>yāriṉum yāriṉu meṉṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When I said I loved her more than any other woman, she said "more than others, yes, more than others," and remained sulky.</l>
